Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,FUCK YES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mangan hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be
