Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:46.28,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1123.555,520)}Game 10\NEast Hand 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada is most probably holding a Pinzu (dots) Honisou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So here, should he discard his 7 Sou (bamboo)?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards the 7 Sou he's one from Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Harada's still full of Pin (dot) tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's careless he may yet deal into Hiroyuki's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a Tatehon hand?(closed single suit)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't amount to a Mangan hand
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets him to Tenpai one turn faster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hiroyuki draws a 1 or 4 Pin, he might just discard it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Harada's in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he wins then the loss to this side should be large
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hiroyuki had discarded a 7 Sou from this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be in Tenpai now with this 1 Pin draw
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He missed the win, didn't he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a mistake at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will change into an entirely DIFFERENT one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A *Junchan **Ryanpeikou???
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:39.12,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,*Junchan: All sets contain a terminal [1 or 9]\N**Ryanpeikou: Two double sequences (here 2x 7, 8, 9 Sou, 2x 1, 2, 3 Pin)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but to get that you'd need to draw another 9 Sou, and he's already using 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could draw someting like that it would be the DEVIL'S OWN LUCK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's truly got no chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My god...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he DREW IT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now they change
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether this hand will be completed is now entrusted to Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's discards show he's certainly got a large hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipeikou Tsumo with 2 Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mangan win
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get a little crazy here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a vision
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of a pounding within the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of a DRAGON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,sunk deep underground
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand's all messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His chance for either Jyunchan or Ryanpeiko just vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
