Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it no use at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DRAGON HAS SPLIT THE EARTH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
