Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. it's still okay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi and Hiroyuki are only just BARELY in the game
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With one hit and we can kick them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU MORON(kansai dialect)!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this fucking mealy mouthed SHIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what that win means!
