Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already decided what we have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As you like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more this looks like the last hand, doesn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's SuuAnKou just now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It lit a fire under their asses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna come at us with everything they got
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't any reasonable contest any more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we eat or be eaten?
