Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's come
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The first Riichi of the last hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a Mangan hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If he draws his tile, it's over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My making a quick hand is best here
