Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This game doesn't have a "no tenpai penalty"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just have to not deal into his hand
